Yes. So they I well, I'm going to talk about the Blockbuster one, because we're going to go that

00:19:07.680 --> 00:19:13.839
way. So they are big structural failures, because there's a big swing that brought something down.

00:19:14.560 --> 00:19:20.079
Rather than they do incorporate, like I said, they're all interconnected. That's why there's

00:19:20.079 --> 00:19:23.599
so many taxonomies of failure. It's impossible to put them all cleanly in one bucket.

00:19:24.719 --> 00:19:32.160
But taking that big swing, they didn't comprehend that where the pieces were. Their new tenure into

00:19:32.880 --> 00:19:40.959
on demand was that brittle piece, right? And that brought down the company. Had their move

