been part of the company, you know, like a metaverse, like we're taking a big swing,

00:19:44.719 --> 00:19:48.719
but we're not putting all our eggs in one basket, people would lose their jobs and it would not be

00:19:48.719 --> 00:19:53.839
a good thing, but it wouldn't bring down the system. And so I put that kind of in a structural.

